&lt;p>Since the first of our life &lt;br>
All parts and systems of our body are designed, &lt;br>
developed, trained, used, and maintained &lt;br>
in such a way that survival of the life is kept &lt;br>
at the helm of everything, we do or create.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Mother nature teaches that to us. &lt;br>
Our parents and friends teach us this. &lt;br>
Our teachers and instructors teach &lt;br>
that to us in the classroom and playground.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>